text: "Strong" is a 1999 song by Robbie Williams and is the third single from his second studio album I've Been Expecting You. It went to number 4 in the United Kingdom and Scotland, number 12 in Ireland, number 9 in New Zealand, number 15 in Poland, number 8 in Hungary, number 7 in Iceland and number 55 in the Netherlands. ==Track listings== UK CD single # "Strong" # "Let Me Entertain You" (live at the Brit Awards '99) # "Happy Song" # "Let Me Entertain You" (live at the Brit Awards '99 video) UK cassette single # "Strong" # "Let Me Entertain You" (live at the Brit Awards '99) # "Happy Song" European CD single # "Strong" # "Let Me Entertain You" (live at the Brit Awards '99) # "Let Me Entertain You" (live at the Brit Awards '99 video) ==References== Category:1999 songs Category:Robbie Williams songs
